ent/uploads/2021/05/21080749/fsa-K-Force-Modular-Supercompact-crankset-gravel-groupset.jpg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/21080749/fsa-K-Force-Modular-Supercompact-crankset-gravel-groupset.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/21080749/fsa-K-Force-Modular-Supercompact-crankset-gravel-groupset-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/21080749/fsa-K-Force-Modular-Supercompact-crankset-gravel-groupset-800x533.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/21080749/fsa-K-Force-Modular-Supercompact-crankset-gravel-groupset-120x80.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/21080749/fsa-K-Force-Modular-Supercompact-crankset-gravel-groupset-768x512.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/21080749/fsa-K-Force-Modular-Supercompact-crankset-gravel-groupset-696x464.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/21080749/fsa-K-Force-Modular-Supercompact-crankset-gravel-groupset-1068x712.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/21080749/fsa-K-Force-Modular-Supercompact-crankset-gravel-groupset-630x420.jpg 630w\"></a><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-259492\">Learn more about FSA’s super compact gearing and ultra-short cranks in a previous Q&amp;A <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2021/03/12/aasq-109-fsa-discuss-ultra-short-cranks-and-super-compact-gearing-for-gravel-bikes/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">here</a></figcaption></figure><p>Fortunately, FSA has been at the forefront of compact and super compact crank designs, adding to the continued development of gravel riding. This goes to prove that there is no one size fits all, silver bullet, or quiver killer set up with so many sub-categories and different needs. Not to mention, cyclists live, ride, and seek out different terrain and experiences.<span data-ez-name=\"bikerumor_com-medrectangle-4\"></span></p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/21080735/fsa-f-force-light-agx-2x-crankset-gravel-drivetrain.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/21080735/fsa-f-force-light-agx-2x-crankset-gravel-drivetrain.jpg\" alt=\"fsa k-force light agx 2x gravel crankset adventure cross\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/21080735/fsa-f-force-light-agx-2x-crankset-gravel-drivetrain.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/21080735/fsa-f-force-light-agx-2x-crankset-gravel-drivetrain-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/21080735/fsa-f-force-light-agx-2x-crankset-gravel-drivetrain-800x533.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/21080735/fsa-f-force-light-agx-2x-crankset-gravel-drivetrain-120x80.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/21080735/fsa-f-force-light-agx-2x-crankset-gravel-drivetrain-768x512.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/21080735/fsa-f-force-light-agx-2x-crankset-gravel-drivetrain-696x464.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/21080735/fsa-f-force-light-agx-2x-crankset-gravel-drivetrain-1068x712.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/21080735/fsa-f-force-light-agx-2x-crankset-gravel-drivetrain-630x420.jpg 630w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb13 src ng ngcb13 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/21080735/fsa-f-force-light-agx-2x-crankset-gravel-drivetrain.jpg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/21080735/fsa-f-force-light-agx-2x-crankset-gravel-drivetrain.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/21080735/fsa-f-force-light-agx-2x-crankset-gravel-drivetrain-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/21080735/fsa-f-force-light-agx-2x-crankset-gravel-drivetrain-800x533.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/21080735/fsa-f-force-light-agx-2x-crankset-gravel-drivetrain-120x80.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/21080735/fsa-f-force-light-agx-2x-crankset-gravel-drivetrain-768x512.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/21080735/fsa-f-force-light-agx-2x-crankset-gravel-drivetrain-696x464.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/21080735/fsa-f-force-light-agx-2x-crankset-gravel-drivetrain-1068x712.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/21080735/fsa-f-force-light-agx-2x-crankset-gravel-drivetrain-630x420.jpg 630w\"></a></p><p>FSA continues to work with professionals who give valuable feedback in developing our products, including our AGX (Adventure Gravel Cross) category, all the while not wanting to keep the status quo on technology and continuing to look for the best fit for all cyclists.</p><p><span data-ez-name=\"bikerumor_com-box-4\"></span><strong>MicroSHIFT: </strong>Gravel is a really big category that covers a lot of different riding styles. Components optimized for competitive gravel racing are going to look different than those for, say, bikepacking or leisurely mixed-terrain group rides. At microSHIFT, we’ve always been intrigued by the idea of wide range 1x drivetrains on bikes with drop bars.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/21082933/microshift-drop-bar-shofter-for-advent-x-10-speed-mtb-drivetrains.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/21082933/microshift-drop-bar-shofter-for-advent-x-10-speed-mtb-drivetrains.jpg\" alt=\"microshift advent x 10 speed drop bar brifters\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/21082933/microshift-drop-bar-shofter-for-advent-x-10-speed-mtb-drivetrains.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/21082933/microshift-drop-bar-shofter-for-advent-x-10-speed-mtb-drivetrains-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/21082933/microshift-drop-bar-shofter-for-advent-x-10-speed-mtb-drivetrains-800x533.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/21082933/microshift-drop-bar-shofter-for-advent-x-10-speed-mtb-drivetrains-120x80.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/21082933/microshift-drop-bar-shofter-for-advent-x-10-speed-mtb-drivetrains-768x512.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/21082933/microshift-drop-bar-shofter-for-advent-x-10-speed-mtb-drivetrains-696x464.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/21082933/microshift-drop-bar-shofter-for-advent-x-10-speed-mtb-drivetrains-1068x712.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/21082933/microshift-drop-bar-shofter-for-advent-x-10-speed-mtb-drivetrains-630x420.jpg 630w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb13 src ng ngcb13 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/21082933/microshift-drop-bar-shofter-for-advent-x-10-speed-mtb-drivetrains.jpg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/21082933/microshift-drop-bar-shofter-for-advent-x-10-speed-mtb-drivetrains.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/21082933/microshift-drop-bar-shofter-for-advent-x-10-speed-mtb-drivetrains-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/21082933/microshift-drop-bar-shofter-for-advent-x-10-speed-mtb-drivetrains-800x533.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/21082933/microshift-drop-bar-shofter-for-advent-x-10-speed-mtb-drivetrains-120x80.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/21082933/microshift-drop-bar-shofter-for-advent-x-10-speed-mtb-drivetrains-768x512.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/21082933/microshift-drop-bar-shofter-for-advent-x-10-speed-mtb-drivetrains-696x464.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/21082933/microshift-drop-bar-shofter-for-advent-x-10-speed-mtb-drivetrains-1068x712.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/21082933/microshift-drop-bar-shofter-for-advent-x-10-speed-mtb-drivetrains-630x420.jpg 630w\"></a></p><p>That’s why we offer 1x integrated drop bar shifters for our ADVENT and ADVENT X mountain bike groups – it can make for a fun, simple setup that is deceptively high performance in a lot of common riding situations. If you want something relatively lightweight with good chain security and a really straightforward, predictable gear progression, these groups hit a pretty nice sweet spot.&nbsp;</p><figure id=\"attachment_234335\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-234335\"><a href=\"http://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Microshift-Advent-X-1-x-10-drivetrain-affordable-shimano-freehub-body-wide-range-cassette-clutch-6.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Microshift-Advent-X-1-x-10-drivetrain-affordable-shimano-freehub-body-wide-range-cassette-clutch-6.jpg\" alt=\"Microshift Advent X 1 x 10 drivetrain affordable shimano freehub body wide range cassette clutch (6)\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1707\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Microshift-Advent-X-1-x-10-drivetrain-affordable-shimano-freehub-body-wide-range-cassette-clutch-6.jpg 2560w,https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Microshift-Advent-X-1-x-10-drivetrain-affordable-shimano-freehub-body-wide-range-cassette-clutch-6-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Microshift-Advent-X-1-x-10-drivetrain-affordable-shimano-freehub-body-wide-range-cassette-clutch-6-800x533.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Microshift-Advent-X-1-x-10-drivetrain-affordable-shimano-freehub-body-wide-range-cassette-clutch-6-120x80.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Microshift-Advent-X-1-x-10-drivetrain-affordable-shimano-freehub-body-wide-range-cassette-clutch-6-768x512.jpg 768w,https://bike